d dairy actions include buying hormone free milk and finding local farmers who can sell meat and eggs directly to you on the seafood front we recommend following the monterey bay aquarium's seafood watch guide the waste category suggest ways to reduce your waste footprint buy recycled products use a reusable coffee mug and start a compost pile in your yard we hope these ideas help you find sustainability from the grocery store to the dinner table fun facts for each section check here for additional fun information tips and quirky facts stanford university school of earth sciences stanford university home school of earth sciences home
